| Trivia                  = * Original set to be released on July 26, 2024, it was then delayed to December 20, 2024.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/disney-moves-avatar-star-wars-avengers-1235514145/|title=‘Avatar 3’ Pushed a Year to 2025, Two ‘Star Wars’ Movies Head for 2026 and ‘Avengers’ Films Delayed|work=The Hollywood Reporter|last=Couch|first=Aaron|date=June 13, 2023|accessdate=June 13, 2023|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20230613153920/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/disney-moves-avatar-star-wars-avengers-1235514145/|archivedate=June 13, 2023}}</ref> But then on November 9, 2023, it was reported that the film had been delayed further to July 25, 2025.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/deadpool-3-release-dates-captain-america-1235643159/|title=‘Deadpool 3’, ‘Captain America 4’ Among Marvel Release Date Changes as Strike Ends|work=The Hollywood Reporter|last=Couch|first=Aaron|date=November 9, 2023|accessdate=November 10, 2023|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20231110010434/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/deadpool-3-release-dates-captain-america-1235643159/|archivedate=November 10, 2023}}</ref> Now the film was scheduled for May 2, 2025.

